I '''Edith Stein''', a kilala murin king lagyung '''St. Teresa Benedicta of the Cross, O.C.D.''' ({{lang-de|Teresia Benedicta vom Kreuz}}, {{lang-la|Teresia Benedicta a cruce}}) (12 Octubre 1891 – 9 Agosto 1942), metung yang Aleman a Hudyong filósofo a mekumbirti king Iglesia Catolica, at kaybat, meging [[madre]]ng  [[Discalced Carmelite]]. Tuturing deng She is regarded as a [[martir]] ampong [[santo]] ning Iglesia Catolica.

Megi yang santo i Stein kapamilatan nang [[Papa Juan Pablo II]] anyang 1998. Metung ya kareng anam a santong patron ning [[Europa]], kayabe ya i San [[Benedicto ning Nursia]], Santo  [[Cyril ampong Methodius]], Santa [[Bridget ning Sweden]] ampong Santa [[Catalina ning Siena]].

